00:32:58,700 --> 00:32:59,180
[Timekeeping Division Report]

566
00:33:00,920 --> 00:33:02,570
The Forestry Division's work

567
00:33:02,830 --> 00:33:04,770
[Forestry Division Report]
is to collect timber for construction projects.

568
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:06,490
Since spring began this year,

569
00:33:06,830 --> 00:33:08,620
we've supplied the palace with rare woods

570
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:10,220
[Forestry Division Report]
such as huanghuali,

571
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:12,250
rosewood, and wenge.

572
00:33:12,550 --> 00:33:13,570
A total of three thousand logs.

573
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:22,770
My Lord,

574
00:33:23,270 --> 00:33:25,620
the Geomancy Division

575
00:33:25,880 --> 00:33:28,420
[Geomancy Division Report]
handles land surveying and soil testing.

576
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:30,860
We assess terrain and locate auspicious burial sites.

577
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:32,980
[Geomancy Division Report]
A pressing matter recently

578
00:33:33,160 --> 00:33:35,180
is the funeral of General Fu Zhisong.

579
00:33:39,310 --> 00:33:39,860
Very good.

580
00:33:40,750 --> 00:33:42,380
Leave all the documents here.

581
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:44,730
Today is my first day in office,

582
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:46,460
and there's still much I need to study.

583
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:48,940
I'll make notes on the documents as needed.

584
00:33:49,270 --> 00:33:50,250
If I have further questions,

585
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:51,490
I'll visit you all privately

586
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:53,700
this afternoon.

587
00:33:54,880 --> 00:33:55,660
You may go now.

588
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:08,210
My Lord,

589
00:34:08,710 --> 00:34:10,130
shall we take a look at the study?

590
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,860
[Reports from Geomancy and Forestry Divisions]
Please instruct us

591
00:34:12,070 --> 00:34:13,340
on its setup and use.

592
00:34:17,710 --> 00:34:18,170
No.

593
00:34:18,550 --> 00:34:19,900
Take me to the Mortuary Division first.

594
00:34:26,590 --> 00:34:28,090
The most delicate mortuary skill

595
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:29,300
is stitching and patching.

596
00:34:29,710 --> 00:34:30,210
For stitching,

597
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:32,380
we use mulberry bark fiber

598
00:34:33,070 --> 00:34:34,340
to sew skin wounds

599
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:35,460
and reattach separated parts.

600
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:39,170
As for patching, usually we use dough.

601
00:34:40,000 --> 00:34:41,530
But General Fu held great rank,

602
00:34:42,480 --> 00:34:44,420
so we'll use sandalwood to restore his body.

603
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:46,010
Understood?

604
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,420
- Yes, My Lord. - Yes, My Lord.

605
00:34:49,710 --> 00:34:51,460
These bones here are all broken.

606
00:34:52,190 --> 00:34:53,260
We'll bind them with copper wire.

607
00:34:57,150 --> 00:34:57,650
Here it is.

608
00:34:58,840 --> 00:34:59,380
Not that.

609
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:00,380
The scissors.

610
00:35:02,030 --> 00:35:02,530
Here it is.

611
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:10,420
My Lord.

612
00:35:11,070 --> 00:35:12,010
- My Lord! - My Lord!

613
00:35:12,190 --> 00:35:13,260
Which of you is Shi Quan?

614
00:35:14,400 --> 00:35:15,170
My Lord, how may I help?

615
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:18,010
I'd like to speak to you alone.

616
00:35:20,630 --> 00:35:21,340
The rest of you, step out.

617
00:35:21,710 --> 00:35:22,460
- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.

618
00:35:34,760 --> 00:35:36,460
My Lord, are you here to question me?

619
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:38,530
Is there anything to question?

620
00:35:40,510 --> 00:35:42,010
The general's body arrived this morning.

621
00:35:42,960 --> 00:35:43,820
It must be prepared immediately.

622
00:35:45,030 --> 00:35:45,900
I hope you'll understand.

623
00:35:47,440 --> 00:35:49,130
His Majesty ordered a grand burial for General Fu.

624
00:35:50,110 --> 00:35:51,610
The body was delayed on the road,

625
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,300
so preparing it early was the right call.

626
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:54,650
It's not winter yet.

627
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:56,050
Even a few hours' difference

628
00:35:56,590 --> 00:35:57,570
can make a big impact.

629
00:36:04,510 --> 00:36:06,170
Just now, were you teaching them?

630
00:36:07,150 --> 00:36:08,130
Why are they the only ones

631
00:36:08,670 --> 00:36:10,050
helping you with such important work?

632
00:36:11,000 --> 00:36:13,210
Mr. Chu said mortuary work isn't demanding,

633
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:16,300
so he cut our division's staff to save costs.

634
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:17,940
I'm usually the only one here.

635
00:36:19,030 --> 00:36:20,980
I just have the apprentices help out.

636
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:23,300
They're from civilian families,

637
00:36:24,070 --> 00:36:25,170
so they're still a bit clumsy.

638
00:36:28,590 --> 00:36:29,300
I'll lend a hand.

639
00:38:07,110 --> 00:38:08,690
I didn't expect you to be this skilled.

640
00:38:10,590 --> 00:38:11,780
I learned this as a child,

641
00:38:12,510 --> 00:38:13,420
but never got the hang of it.

642
00:38:14,630 --> 00:38:15,740
To be good at this,

643
00:38:16,630 --> 00:38:17,900
you need more than talent.

644
00:38:19,150 --> 00:38:20,130
It takes a lot of patience.

645
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:22,090
You're too modest, My Lord.

646
00:38:24,150 --> 00:38:25,860
You've served in the Bureau for many years, right?

647
00:38:26,630 --> 00:38:27,780
Have you always been stationed here?

648
00:38:28,110 --> 00:38:28,610
My Lord,

649
00:38:29,150 --> 00:38:30,420
no need to be so polite with me.

650
00:38:30,960 --> 00:38:32,170
Say what's on your mind.

651
00:38:32,630 --> 00:38:33,530
Did you come to the Astronomical Bureau

652
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:35,260
to make a fortune,

653
00:38:35,550 --> 00:38:36,900
or just to climb the ranks?

654
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:38,530
I don't really care.

655
00:38:39,440 --> 00:38:40,380
I only hope

656
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:42,130
you'll let me work in peace

657
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:43,820
and focus on my duties.

658
00:39:18,220 --> 00:39:20,620
[Zang Residence]

659
00:39:20,710 --> 00:39:21,650
Make sure this courtyard

660
00:39:21,670 --> 00:39:22,900
is spotless every day,

661
00:39:23,030 --> 00:39:23,860
not a speck of dust left behind.

662
00:39:24,630 --> 00:39:25,900
It's Mr. Zang's first day in office.

663
00:39:26,480 --> 00:39:27,090
Inform the kitchen,

664
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:29,340
tonight's meal must be perfect!

665
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:30,570
Understood?

666
00:39:31,590 --> 00:39:32,050
From now on,

667
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:32,860
all of you...

668
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:33,530
- My Lord. - My Lord.

669
00:39:34,670 --> 00:39:35,090
My Lord.

670
00:39:36,150 --> 00:39:36,460
Enough.

671
00:39:37,030 --> 00:39:37,980
Off you go, now.

672
00:39:44,110 --> 00:39:44,610
You're back!

673
00:39:46,630 --> 00:39:47,570
I met all the officials

674
00:39:47,590 --> 00:39:48,490
at the Astronomical Bureau today...

675
00:39:48,510 --> 00:39:49,380
Don't talk about that yet.

676
00:39:49,960 --> 00:39:50,490
Turn around first.

677
00:39:51,630 --> 00:39:52,570
Go on, turn!

678
00:39:58,590 --> 00:39:59,260
Take a few steps.

679
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:01,460
Master...

680
00:40:04,670 --> 00:40:06,900
This outfit suits you well.

681
00:40:08,590 --> 00:40:10,130
The first clothes you wore in the Capital

682
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:11,860
were the ones I got for you.

683
00:40:13,440 --> 00:40:14,820
Now you're in full official robes.

684
00:40:16,030 --> 00:40:16,570
Looks good.

685
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:19,900
If Xing Dou saw you now,

686
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:21,210
he'd probably complain

687
00:40:21,230 --> 00:40:22,340
that one sleeve's longer.

688
00:40:24,440 --> 00:40:25,740
So, how did it go today?

689
00:40:28,670 --> 00:40:29,780
The Bureau now

690
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:31,690
is nothing like

691
00:40:32,230 --> 00:40:33,210
when my father was in charge.

692
00:40:34,760 --> 00:40:36,900
Back then, everyone had their role,

693
00:40:37,190 --> 00:40:38,090
and got along well.

694
00:40:38,840 --> 00:40:40,170
If my father could help,

695
00:40:40,510 --> 00:40:41,740
he always would.

696
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:46,050
But now, everyone wears a mask.

697
00:40:46,670 --> 00:40:47,490
There's no sincerity left.

698
00:40:48,280 --> 00:40:49,490
What nonsense!

699
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:51,010
Your father

700
00:40:51,030 --> 00:40:52,380
was just a man who ran funeral business.

701
00:40:52,670 --> 00:40:54,380
He had nothing to do with the Bureau.

702
00:40:59,230 --> 00:41:00,820
Now that you hold office,

703
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:03,460
you're not just an aide from the Marquis's Mansion anymore.

704
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:05,210
More eyes are on you.

705
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:06,610
Back at the Marquis's Mansion,

706
00:41:07,110 --> 00:41:08,900
as long as he trusted you, it was enough.

707
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:10,610
But in court,

708
00:41:11,480 --> 00:41:13,260
daggers come from every direction.

709
00:41:13,840 --> 00:41:15,170
You'll need to be more careful.

710
00:41:17,070 --> 00:41:17,820
You're right, Master.

711
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:19,690
The Bureau today

712
00:41:19,920 --> 00:41:21,820
is full of opportunists and spies.

713
00:41:22,670 --> 00:41:24,690
I'm afraid the road ahead won't be smooth.

714
00:41:26,280 --> 00:41:27,530
When Chu Huaiming was in charge,

715
00:41:28,070 --> 00:41:29,780
the Bureau served the wicked many times.

716
00:41:30,030 --> 00:41:30,900
I've heard of those stories.

717
00:41:31,800 --> 00:41:34,130
Ever hear about the missing daughter of the Lin family?

718
00:41:37,070 --> 00:41:38,340
That was three years ago.

719
00:41:40,110 --> 00:41:42,460
The Lin family's girl had just turned thirteen.

720
00:41:43,110 --> 00:41:45,490
But Duke E's eldest son fancied her.

721
00:41:45,760 --> 00:41:46,780
He insisted on making her his concubine.

722
00:41:47,630 --> 00:41:48,380
But he

723
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:50,210
was thirty years older than her.

724
00:41:51,110 --> 00:41:52,260
The Lin family flatly refused.

725
00:41:53,070 --> 00:41:53,980
Strangely enough,

726
00:41:54,320 --> 00:41:56,690
that young master died

727
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:57,650
from overdosing.

728
00:41:58,550 --> 00:42:00,570
The Lin family thought it was over,

729
00:42:01,840 --> 00:42:04,380
until three days after his death,

730
00:42:05,510 --> 00:42:07,210
their daughter suddenly vanished.

731
00:42:08,110 --> 00:42:09,380
Guess where they found her?

732
00:42:10,230 --> 00:42:10,780
Where?

733
00:42:11,550 --> 00:42:13,170
In the tomb of Duke E's son.

734
00:42:14,230 --> 00:42:15,650
She'd been strangled,

735
00:42:15,760 --> 00:42:17,380
wearing a bridal gown.

736
00:42:19,230 --> 00:42:22,210
Her poor parents went mad with grief.

737
00:42:22,440 --> 00:42:24,860
But the Great Yong law clearly forbids ghost marriages!

738
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:27,570
That rule only applies to commoners.

739
00:42:28,550 --> 00:42:31,650
The court turns a blind eye when it's nobles.

740
00:42:32,590 --> 00:42:33,460
That ghost marriage

741
00:42:34,230 --> 00:42:35,380
might've been arranged

742
00:42:35,630 --> 00:42:37,010
by the Astronomical Bureau!

743
00:42:39,480 --> 00:42:40,210
And not just that.

744
00:42:40,550 --> 00:42:41,340
Last October,

745
00:42:41,670 --> 00:42:44,090
under the guise of aiding nobles,

746
00:42:44,710 --> 00:42:47,460
the Bureau took over every orchard in Wang Village.

747
00:42:48,840 --> 00:42:49,980
Left with nowhere to appeal,

748
00:42:50,400 --> 00:42:52,820
those poor farmers were forced from their homes.

749
00:42:54,070 --> 00:42:54,940
This Bureau

750
00:42:55,590 --> 00:42:57,130
is long overdue for a clean-up.

751
00:43:22,260 --> 00:43:26,940
♪Conceal the ambition in my eyes♪

752
00:43:29,460 --> 00:43:36,100
♪In my palm, I hold a dangerous desire♪

753
00:43:36,660 --> 00:43:39,420
♪Turbulent waves hidden in my sleeves♪

754
00:43:40,020 --> 00:43:42,740
♪Silent thunder echoes around♪

755
00:43:43,020 --> 00:43:44,980
♪However cunning you are♪

756
00:43:45,460 --> 00:43:47,540
♪I can see♪

757
00:43:49,260 --> 00:43:51,380
♪Right through you♪

758
00:43:57,740 --> 00:44:04,780
♪Schemes are my armor♪

759
00:44:04,940 --> 00:44:10,380
♪Overt plans are my weapons♪

760
00:44:11,940 --> 00:44:14,660
♪With restrained fury♪

761
00:44:15,340 --> 00:44:18,020
♪I purge the world's corruption♪

762
00:44:18,220 --> 00:44:20,260
♪The night is not dark♪

763
00:44:20,740 --> 00:44:22,820
♪Because♪

764
00:44:23,940 --> 00:44:29,420
♪My heart burns bright♪

765
00:44:32,220 --> 00:44:35,500
♪I control the shifting clouds♪

766
00:44:35,700 --> 00:44:38,260
♪I command the falling rain♪

767
00:44:38,420 --> 00:44:40,780
♪The compass of the human soul is unpredictable♪

768
00:44:40,900 --> 00:44:45,700
♪There will always be ups and downs♪

769
00:44:46,180 --> 00:44:49,500
♪I hold the power of life and death♪

770
00:44:49,700 --> 00:44:52,260
♪I grant and I take away♪

771
00:44:52,420 --> 00:44:55,940
♪When faith burns like the scorching sun♪

772
00:44:55,980 --> 00:44:59,460
♪I will sing aloud with you♪

773
00:44:59,580 --> 00:45:02,820
♪I am the sowing season♪

774
00:45:02,940 --> 00:45:06,220
♪I am the autumn harvest♪

775
00:45:06,460 --> 00:45:08,620
♪I am the world♪

776
00:45:08,820 --> 00:45:12,380
♪I am the people♪

777
00:45:13,580 --> 00:45:16,660
♪And you are also me♪
